##   required Studio level (e.g. SP_RACE_4 = 50,000 RP at Lv3, cap was 1,600), so those projects could
##   NEVER be researched. get_rnd_rp_storage_cap() is now DYNAMIC: 15% above the priciest P4/P5 project
